             was indicted for <rs id="t18050529-45-off242" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18050529-45-off242" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050529-45-off242" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18050529-45-cd243" type="crimeDate">29th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050529-45-off242 t18050529-45-cd243"></join>, a pair of shoes, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18050529-45-victim406" type="victimName">
                  Richard 
                  Bickerton
               <interp inst="t18050529-45-victim406" type="surname" value="Bickerton"></interp>
